<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 35 (September 11, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Feeding Frenzy (Q)</b></li><ul><li> The Power ratio of the initial part of this ability has been reduced to 0.7, down from 0.8.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 34 (August 19th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Feeding Frenzy (Q)</b></li><ul><li>The base damage on this ability has been reduced to 50/95/140/185/230, down from 60/105/150/195/240.</li><li>The Power ratio on this ability has been increased to 0.8, up from 0.7.</li></ul><li><b>Tidal Prison (E)</b></li><ul><li>The base damage of this ability has been reduced to 65/115/165/215/265, down from 80/130/180/230/180.</li><li>The tooltip for this ability now correctly reflects the duration of the slowing effect.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 30 (May 27th, 2014)</h4><p>Amarynth's spirit regeneration now scales with Haste at a rate of 1% increased regeneration per 1% cooldown reduction granted by Haste.</p><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 29 (May 5th, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Amarynth's visual and sound effects on her abilities have been updated.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Feeding Frenzy (Q)</li><ul><li>The range of this ability has been increased by 11%</li><li>The Power ratio of this ability has been reduced to 0.7, down from 1.0.</li><li>The Power ratio of the damage over time component of this ability has been reduced to 0.6, down from 0.8.</li><li>The base damage of the damage over time component of this ability has been reduced to 50/80/110/140/170, down from 80/120/160/200/240.</li></ul><li>Waverider (W)</li><ul><li>The range of this ability has been increased by 6%.</li><li>The Power ratio of this ability has been reduced to 0.6, down from 0.8.</li></ul><li>Tidal Prison (E)</li><ul><li>The range of this ability has been increased by 3%.</li><li>The Power ratio of this ability has been reduced to 0.75, down from 0.95.</li></ul><li>Riptide (R)</li><ul><li>The range of this ability has been increased by 6%.</li><li>The Power ratio of this ability has been reduced to 0.8, down from 1.2.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 19 (November 27, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Fixed a bug that was causing Amarynth to occasionally fire multiple instances of her abilities.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 10 (August 23, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Base Movement Speed reduced to 380, down from 385.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 8 (August 09, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Feeding Frenzy (Q)</B></li><ul><li>The cast time of this ability has been increased to 0.4 seconds, up from 0.2 seconds.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 5 (July 18, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Feeding Frenzy (Q)</B></li><ul><li>The base damage of this ability has been reduced to 60/105/150/195/240, down from 60/110/160/210/260.</li></ul><li><B>Riptide (R)</B></li><ul><li>The power ratio on this ability has been reduced to 1.2 per point of Power, down from 1.4 per point of Power.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 3 (June 21, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Riptide (R)</B></li><ul><li>Increased the height of the projectile to fix an issue with certain Shapers being able to jump over it and avoid the damage.</li></ul></ul>